## cv识别手写数字

```python
import cv2 as cv
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
```

```python
img1 = cv.imread("./mnist/pic_5.png")
img2 = cv.resize(img1,(28,28))
img3 = cv.cvtColor(img2, cv.COLOR_RGB2GRAY)
img3=255-img3
img3=img3*(img3>255/2)
tran=torchvision.transforms.ToTensor()
img4=tran(img3)
output1 = net(img4, 1)
plt.imshow(img3)
output1.data.max(1, keepdim=True)[1],img4.shape
#(tensor([[5]]), torch.Size([1, 28, 28]))
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```python
img1 = cv.imread("./mnist/pic_520.png")
img2 = cv.cvtColor(img1, cv.COLOR_RGB2GRAY)
img2=(255-img2)*((255-img2)>255/2)
contours,hierarchy=cv.findContours(img2,cv.RETR_EXTERNAL, cv.CHAIN_APPROX_SIMPLE)
cv.drawContours(img1,contours,-1,255)
plt.imshow(img1)
```

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```python
res=[]
tran=torchvision.transforms.ToTensor()
for i in range(len(contours)):
    x,y,w,h=cv.boundingRect(contours[i])
    img3=img2[y:y+h,x:x+w]
    img3=cv.copyMakeBorder(img3,15,15,15,15,cv.BORDER_CONSTANT,0)
    img3=cv.resize(img3,(28,28))
    img3=tran(img3)
    res.append(net(img3,1).data.max(1, keepdim=True)[1][0].tolist()[0])
res.sort(reverse=True)
#'[5, 2, 0]'
```
